;www.baidu.com.			IN	A

;; ANSWER SECTION:
www.baidu.com.		5	IN	CNAME	www.a.shifen.com.
www.a.shifen.com.	5	IN	A	14.215.177.38
www.a.shifen.com.	5	IN	A	14.215.177.39

;; Query time: 44 msec
