编译安装bind9:
		前提：准备编译环境
			"Development Tools", "Server Platform Development"
		获取源代码，解压源代码;
			INSTALL, README
			./configure 
			make
			make
		1、编译安装bind9.10：（确保rpm包格式的bind未安装）
			# groupadd -r -g 53 named
			# useradd -r -g named -u 53 named
			# ./configure --prefix=/usr/local/bind9 --sysconfdir=/etc/named/ --disable-ipv6 --disable-chroot --enable-threads
			# make && make install
			后续的步骤：
			1、导出程序路径至PATH中；
			2、导出帮助文件；
			3、库文件和头文件；
		2、提供基本的区域解析库
			# mkdir /var/named
			# cd /var/named
			2.1 named.ca
				# dig -t NS . @SERVER_IP > named.ca
			2.2 named.localhost
				$TTL 86400
				@	IN	SOA	localhost.	nsadmin.localhost. (
						2014121101
						12H
						1H
						15D
						1D )
					IN	NS	localhost.
					IN	A	127.0.0.1
			2.3 named.loopback
				$TTL 86400
				@	IN	SOA	localhost.	nsadmin.localhost. (
						2014121101
						12H
						1H
						15D
						1D )
					IN	NS	localhost.
				1	IN	PTR	localhost.

		3、提供配置文件
			3.1 rndc.conf
				# rndc-confgen -r /dev/urandom > /etc/named/rndc.conf
			3.2 named.conf
				options {
					directory "/var/named";
				};

				zone "." IN {
					type hint;
					file "named.ca";
				};

				zone "localhost" IN {
					type master;
					file "named.localhost";
					allow-update { none; };
				};

				zone "0.0.127.in-addr.arpa" IN {
					type master;
					file "named.loopback";
					allow-update { none; };
				};

		4、测试启动
			# named -u named -g [-c /path/to/config_file]
		5、提供服务脚本
